Overlaps with list of alzheimers genes from Gemma (AD GWAS 2021 - Bellenguez, +APOE)

There are 78 unique genes in the list of alzheimers genes from Gemma. However 9 of these do not have a mouse analoge, leaving 69 genes for comparison

The tables below shows how many of these genes are also annotated to a significant site in the RRBS and array data results files
